lamco-rdp-server (1.4.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release
  * Session health monitoring with D-Bus signal relay
  * ext-data-control-v1 / wlr-data-control-v1 clipboard backends
  * View-only mode (ScreenCast-only strategy)
  * OpenH264 dynamic loading with dual ABI support
  * Graceful shutdown (SIGTERM handling, explicit PipeWire cleanup)
  * MSRV raised to 1.88

